      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROTHER BILO (7) goes very well this course and distance starting eight times for four wins and two minors. Recorded a 1.75 lengths win (19.48) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. ONE MARGARITA (1) started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a strong early split, giving a sight but fading only late to finish second (16.94) at this track over 300m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to be in the finish again. TECHNO KELLI (3) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when third (16.88) at Murray Bridge in a Special conditions race. Hits the ground running and will be in the firing line early. Expected to do much better this time. YARRAMUNDI OPAL (5) generally performs well over this distance.",
